        "text": "When thou didst terrible things . . .",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—The latter clause, “thou camest down ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": ". . .",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
